text: hm, i feel like i’ve heard of this before but recall being underwhelmed in the past by it (maybe i’m thinking of something else?), though what they promote currently seems worth checking out. i think it’s really interesting that all these prototyping tools that sucked in the past have seemingly revamped their offerings into something worthwhile over the past year
